public class Stitching
extends java.lang.Object
implements au.gov.ansto.bragg.echidna.dra.processor.ConcreteProcessor

This class is the concrete processor of the stitching algorithm for echidna algorithm group. It uses the stitched data of the echidna input data object. It will return a two-dimensional data which has the integrated vector, the error vector and the two-theta vector.
